Package com.barchart.feed.ddf.message.enums

Enum Summary
DDF_Condition market condition.
DDF_Indicator ddf quote session indicator : "current combo" vs "previous combo" vs "individual session"; possible format: "combined", is combo for today; "previous", is combo for yesterday; "session_D_S", individual (non-combo) day/session permutations; with D=DDF_TradeDay, S=DDF_Session; allows to classify quote snapshot sessions: THIS vs PAST market day.
DDF_MessageType subset of supported ddf messages.
DDF_ParamElement qualifier for market parameter message.
DDF_ParamModifier qualifier for market parameter message.
DDF_ParamType subset of supported market parameter message qualifiers.
DDF_ParamType.Kind The Enum Kind.
DDF_QuoteMode optional xml quote field.
DDF_QuoteState ddf quote state transitions.
DDF_Session ddf trade session source;.
DDF_TradeDay ddf trade day codes.
